liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Some important ins and outs for both sides. Darcy Moore is back for Collingwood, and both Michael Hibberd and Tom McDonald return for the Dees. John Noble is the most unlucky of all to miss out, left out as Beau McCreery comes in and with Oleg Markov preferred for the Pies. Jack Ginnivan is sub for Collingwood and Bailey Laurie for Melbourne.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: Tonight's teams and subs confirmed

children.content: Some important ins and outs for both sides.

Darcy Moore is back for Collingwood, and both Michael Hibberd and Tom McDonald return for the Dees. John Noble is the most unlucky of all to miss out, left out as Beau McCreery comes in and with Oleg Markov preferred for the Pies.
Jack Ginnivan is sub for Collingwood and Bailey Laurie for Melbourne.
